ygData.messageBody:
Last night I ran into a vendor that was selling sketches. His shop was
located within High Pass Hold. I'm sorry I can't tell you more, I was
concentrating on getting through the pass without getting jumped by the
Gnolls or Orcs.

Farin the Travelling Barbarian
